'''AeronautX Luftfahrtschule''' is an [[airline pilot]] school created in 1998 and located at [[Linz Airport]]<ref>[http://www.pilotenausbildung.net/aeronautx-luftfahrtschule-gmbh/ AeronautX Luftfahrtschule GmbH]</ref>.
The school has a partnership with the airline [[Niki (airline)|Niki]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flyniki.com/de/niki/pilot_training.php?name=pilottraining |title=Mit NIKI ins Cockpit |access-date=2017-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815023700/http://www.flyniki.com/de/niki/pilot_training.php?name=pilottraining |archive-date=2017-08-15 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> in order to train ab initio pilots and with the [[Embry–Riddle Aeronautical University]] for a double-degree [[Bachelor's degree|Bachelor]]-[[Airline Transport Pilot Licence|ATPL]]<ref>[http://www.verkehrspilotenstudium.com/en/flightschools/aeronautx.html Our Austrian training partner AeronautX]</ref>.
